The Mercedes in any case does not care too much: the Constructors 'World Championship arrived mathematically at Suzuka, when Stuttgart also had the certainty that the Drivers' Championship will be an internal affair, since Valtteri Bottas remains the only potential opponent of Lewis Hamilton , which in Mexico has further extended and unless sporting cataclysms will celebrate Sunday already. Certainly, Ferrari's growth especially in the dry lap questions Stuttgart, which got its last pole position at the end of July at Hockenheim. In 2020, this will have triggered the alarm for Toto Wolff, but the strong position of the Silver Arrows remains very solid and the ability to exploit the slightest possibility and error of others remains phenomenal. Finally we will see what role Max Verstappen and Red Bull will play in the United States, with the Dutch being the great rival of the two Ferrari drivers for third place in the Drivers' standings. The wait for what will happen in this tantalizing weekend is finally coming to an end, so now let's get comfortable: the direct Formula 1 of the free practice FP1 and FP2 of the United States Usa Grand Prix 2019 in Austin is about to begin ...

